race.description: Queensland Cotton Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: DON'T SAY DO (12) was ridden quietly in a small field then closed reasonably well without ever looking a threat first-up over 1000m at Scone. Won't find this maiden as tough and the extra trip is ideal. Looks a serious chance. UNSOLVED (5) is yet to fill a placing in three career runs, the latest a well-beaten ninth over 1200m at Coonabarabran. Well placed here to finally crack the top three. I'M A HOTTIE (8) the latest effort a fourth over 1000m at Tamworth two months ago. Better effort last time and in the mix. MEGAPHONE MISS (10) is in the mix off a one-month freshen up as is BINDAREE LASS (6) who ran a better race last start to finish second at Narromine over 1100m.
